iption\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:335:\"Now that Autoptimize has had &#8220;critical CSS&#8221; for over 2 years, it is time to let the old &#8220;Autoptimize Criticalcss.com Power-Up&#8221; which still has over 10K active installs finally go pining for the fjords. I pushed out an update for it which will see it deactivate itself if Autoptimize is at version 2.7 or higher.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"futtta\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:463:\"<p>Now that Autoptimize has had &ldquo;critical CSS&rdquo; for over 2 years, it is time to let the old &ldquo;Autoptimize Criticalcss.com Power-Up&rdquo; which still has over 10K active installs finally go pining for the fjords. I pushed out an update for it which will see it deactivate itself if Autoptimize is at version 2.7 or higher.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2022/04/15/criticalcss-power-up-pining-for-the-fjords/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Source</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2022/04/15/criticalcss-power-up-pining-for-the-fjords/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n				